my oath
Homonym Number:
Word Class: exclamation
Sense Number:
Definition:certainly! an exclamation of assent or enthusiasm
Origin: [none]
Register: informal

Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
See: also my colonial oath ; bloody oath
